data.description: Welcome home to a beautiful  5/2/1 in a desirable family-oriented neighborhood located within walking distance of  school, close to shopping , hospitals and major highway.  Relax and sip your morning coffee from a tastefully updated and spacious kitchen with a breakfast nook overlooking private screened-in pool or have  easy conversations with your family from den in this open, bright  and airy living area with marble tiles. Home features a huge master suite with a large walk-in  closet, spacious rooms, plenty of storage space and many other desirable features. Keep your family active at clubhouse overlooking the lake with amenities such as: tennis courts, basket ball court, playground, gym, and a community pool. Do not miss out on this opportunity, you will fall in love with this home.
